text: Arsenal Fútbol Club (), usually referred as Arsenal de Sarandí , is an Argentine sports club from Sarandí, Avellaneda Partido, Greater Buenos Aires. It is best known for its football team. They won their first Primera División championship in 2012 and the Copa Sudamericana in 2007. They are also known for having a similar name to the famous English Premier League team Arsenal F.C ==Honours== ===Domestic=== *Primera División (1): 2012 Clausura * Copa Argentina (1): 2012–13 *Supercopa Argentina (1): 2012 *Primera C (1): 1964 *Primera D (1): 1962 ===International=== *Copa Sudamericana (1): 2007 *Suruga Bank Championship (1): 2008 Category:Football clubs in Buenos Aires Province Category:1957 establishments
title: Arsenal de Sarandí
